body:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Important Security Alert: Phishing Activity Detected</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  h1 {
    color: #d9534f; /* Red for alert */
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h2 {
    color: #337ab7; /* Blue for emphasis */
    margin-top: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  p {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  strong {
    color: #f0ad4e; /* Orange for caution */
  }
  .highlight {
    background-color: #fff3cd;
    padding: 10px;
    border-left: 4px solid #f0ad4e;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: #777;
  }
  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #5cb85c; /* Green for action */
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .button:hover {
    background-color: #4cae4c;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>🚨 IMPORTANT SECURITY ALERT 🚨</h1>

    <p>Dear User,</p>

    <p>We are writing to alert you about an increase in <strong>phishing activities</strong> targeting our users. Phishing is a type of online fraud where attackers impersonate legitimate organizations or individuals to trick you into revealing sensitive information such as usernames, passwords, credit card details, or other personal data.</p>

    <h2>What is Phishing?</h2>
    <p>Phishing attempts often come in the form of emails, text messages, or fake websites that look genuine. They may:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create a sense of urgency, demanding immediate action.</li>
      <li>Ask you to click on suspicious links.</li>
      <li>Request personal or financial information.</li>
      <li>Contain grammatical errors or unusual sender addresses.</li>
      <li>Offer prizes or unexpected rewards.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="highlight">
      <strong>Your security is our top priority.</strong> It is crucial to remain vigilant and aware of these threats to protect yourself and your information.
    </div>

    <h2>How to Protect Yourself:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Be Skeptical:</strong> Always question unsolicited emails or messages, especially those asking for personal information or requesting urgent action.</li>
      <li><strong>Verify Senders:</strong> Carefully check the sender's email address. Look for misspellings or unusual domain names.</li>
      <li><strong>Do Not Click Suspicious Links:</strong> Hover over links (without clicking) to see the actual URL. If it looks suspicious, do not click it.</li>
      <li><strong>Never Share Sensitive Information:</strong> Legitimate organizations will rarely ask for your password, social security number, or full credit card details via email.</li>
      <li><strong>Use Strong, Unique Passwords:</strong> Employ complex passwords for all your online accounts and consider using a password manager.</li>
      <li><strong>Enable Two-Factor Authentication (2FA):</strong> Where available, enable 2FA for an extra layer of security.</li>
      <li><strong>Report Suspicious Activity:</strong> If you receive a suspicious email that appears to be from us, please do not reply or click any links. Forward it to our dedicated security team at <a href="mailto:security@example.com">security@example.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We are continuously working to protect our systems and users from these threats. Your cooperation in being cautious and reporting suspicious activities is invaluable in this effort.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your attention to this important matter.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>The Security Team<br>
    [Your Company Name]</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2023 [Your Company Name]. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated security alert. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
```
